ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectOrder Directing that a Proclamation be issued to set the day on which the people of Canada honour the memory of Her late Majesty Queen Elizabeth the Second
PrecisOrder directing that a PROCLAMATION be issued requesting that the people of Canada set aside September 19, 2022 as the day on which they honour the MEMORY OF HER LATE MAJESTY QUEEN ELIZABETH THE SECOND, who passed away on September 8, 2022.
